snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Pre-Release Event Announcement Trailer | Rishab Shetty | NTR | ShreyasMedia
snippet.description:
Watch Kantara Chapter 1 Pre-Release Event Announcement Trailer on #ShreyasMedia 


#KantaraChapter1PreReleaseEvent #AnnouncementTrailer
#KantaraChapter1 #RishabShetty #Kantara #ALegend #DivineEpic #VijayKiragandu #AjaneeshLoknath #RukminiVasanth #GulshanDevaiah #Jayaram #KantaraTrailer #KantaraChapter1Trailer #Kantarachapter1onOct2 #KantaraTeluguTrailer #KantaraChapter1TeluguTrailer 

The makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar â€” and the visionary, National Awardâ€“winning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend â€“ Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend â€“ Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies, and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025. 

Movie Credits-
Studio: Hombale Films 
Produced by: Vijay Kiragandur
Written and Directed by: Rishab Shetty
Cast: Rishab Shetty, Rukmini Vasanth, Jayaram, Gulshan Devaiah
Director of Photography: Arvind S Kashyap, ISC
Co-Writers: Anirudh Mahesh, Shanil Gowtham
Music & Background Score: B Ajaneesh Loknath
Production Designer: Banglan
Costume Designer: Pragathi Shetty
Art Director: Dharani Gangeputra
Executive Producer: Adarsh J A, Pramod Shetty
Marketing & Branding Partner - Mythri Media Works

snippet.title: Tumse Behtar | Varun D, Janhvi K, Sanya M, Rohit S | Tanishk B, Arijit S, Manoj M | SSKTK
snippet.description:
Youâ€™ve seen them dance, youâ€™ve seen them fall in love, now witness the heartbreak when love gets intertwined! Presenting â€˜Tumse Behtarâ€™ from â€˜Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumariâ€™, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and written by Manoj Muntashir, this beautiful song is sung by Arijit Singh.

#TumseBehtar #ArijitSingh #TanishkBagchi #SSKTK

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singhâ€™s Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:
Tumhara-mera milna likha to hoga kahin
Naseebon ka sitara, mila to hoga Kahin

Na Jane kyun ae humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Raaton me, bina tumhare ghabrayein, ghabraayein
Khwaabon me, milo agar khush ho jaayein ho jaayein

Chain ho tum aaram ho shayad
Koi sukoon ki shaam ho shayad
Khushi kahoon ya dil ki tasalli
Kya tumhein doon main naam

Kitabein dekhi saari, mili na koi shaayri
Tareefein karoon kaise, yahi hai muhskil meri

Na Jane kyun a humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi
Jo daraeyin wo hawayein gham ki, tham jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Dekho na ye kamaal hua hai
Aesa dil ka haal hua hai
Dil mera tere itar me dooba
Jaise koi roomal hua hai

Aesi hai khwahish dil me mere
Jaane mujhe sab naam se tere
Aesi diwangi pahle nahin thee
Haal ye pichhle saal hua hai

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Koi nahin tumse behtar, tumse pyaara
Tumse zyaada mera koi nahin!

snippet.title: Mango Pachcha Teaser | Sanchii | Viveka | KRG Studios | Supriyanvi Studio | CharanRaj | KRG Connects
snippet.description:
The upcoming collaborative biggie of KRG Studios and Supriyanvi Picture Studio #Sanchii01 has revealed its title through a promo of the lead actor Sanchii on account of his birthday. This promo unveils the character of the lead actor and the title of the film. 

"MANGO PACHCHA" is a film that tells the story of an unapologetically ambitious and adventurous man in the city of Mysuru. Based on various real events between the 90â€™s and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.

en.title: Mango Pachcha Teaser | Sanchii | Viveka | KRG Studios | Supriyanvi Studio | CharanRaj | KRG Connects
en.description:
The upcoming collaborative biggie of KRG Studios and Supriyanvi Picture Studio #Sanchii01 has revealed its title through a promo of the lead actor Sanchii on account of his birthday. This promo unveils the character of the lead actor and the title of the film. 

"MANGO PACHCHA" is a film that tells the story of an unapologetically ambitious and adventurous man in the city of Mysuru. Based on various real events between the 90â€™s and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.
